Our study had limitations. The survey was con-
ducted on-site with the hospital staff; therefore,
it is difficult to avoid response or observation
bias. The study was limited to the Zhejiang
Province of China, and it may not represent the
current TB infection control situation in the
central or western provinces of China. In add-
ition, owing to the small sample size, we could
